snippet.description:
九个月前，我用长毛的臭豆腐腌制的红油腐乳，现在终于可以吃了～
豆腐乳是我们当地一道特别美味的家常菜，吃法也很多样～蘸馒头饵块，拌稀饭，打蘸水，拌时蔬，蒸扣肉，炖猪蹄……都特别美味，你们一定要试试～

※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

Nine months ago, I made some fermented bean curd with chili sauce with stinky hairy tofu and now it's ready to eat. Fermented bean curd is a tasty specialty here in our area, with various cooking methods. You can use it as a dipping sauce for steamed buns and erkuai, mix it with porridge, make it into dipping chilies, serve as a seasoning for vegetables, steamed braised meat or stewed pig trotters. Every dish is so tasty with fermented bean curd, be sure to try it out!
